                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    Ignitia is dedicated to protecting forests and communities through cutting-edge artificial intelligence 
                    and satellite technology. Our platform combines machine learning algorithms with real-time environmental 
                    data to provide accurate wildfire risk predictions and fire spread simulations.
                </p>
                
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>
                    Our system analyzes multiple environmental factors including vegetation health (NDVI), land surface 
                    temperature, topographical features, weather conditions, and historical fire patterns. Using advanced 
                    machine learning models trained on extensive satellite imagery and climate data, Ignitia can predict 
                    fire-prone areas and simulate fire spread patterns with high accuracy.
                </p>
                
                <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
                <ul class="tech-list">
