                    <li><strong>Weather Data:</strong> OpenWeatherMap API, ERA5 Reanalysis</li>
                    <li><strong>Geospatial Analysis:</strong> GDAL, Rasterio, GeoPandas</li>
                    <li><strong>Web Platform:</strong> Node.js, Express, EJS, Leaflet.js</li>
                </ul>
